data.description: NO MANDATORY HOA perfect for just about anything!!!! Ideally located near shopping, 5 min drive to Downtown Delray, The Beach and fine dining. This charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home features an open floor plan, 4 large sliding doors in the living room area that brings in a lot of natural light. Title and laminate wood floors throughout living, dining area, and laminate wood floors in the bedrooms Just missing your personal touches and to call it home.ASK ABOUT OUR SELLER CONTRIBUTION.
